  EffectDiscription_ENG: While you have a Digimon with [Armor Form] in its traits
    in play, you may use this card without meeting its color requirements.[Main]
    1 of your opponent's Digimon gets -4000 DP for the turn, and all of your opponent's
    Digimon get -1000 DP for the turn for each card with [Armor Form] in its traits
    in your trash.
